The '''Intergalactic Zoological Society''' ('''IZS''') was devoted to gathering and studying lifeforms from all over [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. It was based on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Mycroft]] and worked with the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Exploration Corps/Legends|Exploration Corps]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the Society refused to take sides, insisting that politics should remain out of science and that knowledge belonged to everyone.

The Society operated a number of exploration ships, including the ''[[Titavian IV]]''.

During the time of the Empire, the IZS held a rivalry with the [[Imperial Environmental Preservation & Refocusing Authority]] (IEPRA) due to the latter's tendency to wipe out any non-sentient lifeforms that were deemed dangerous.

